# Meme Game 2026

A fun browser-based meme game built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project is deployed on AWS S3 as a static website.

## Live Demo
[Play the game here](http://my-meme-game-2026.s3-website-us-west-2.amazonaws.com)

## About the Project
This is my first GitHub project. I created this meme game to practice web development, project deployment, and GitHub documentation.

## Features
- Meme-based browser game
- Easy to access online
- Fast static hosting on AWS S3

## Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- AWS S3

## How to Use
1. Click the live demo link.
2. Launch the game in your browser.
3. Play and enjoy.

## What I Learned
- How to build a simple frontend project
- How to host a website on AWS S3
- How to document a project on GitHub

